gime%20vs%20New%20Regime%3F%20Top%20Questions%20Answered%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20clarify%20that%20the%20income%20mentioned%20here%20is%20the%20taxable%20amount%20since%20taxpayers%20also%20enjoy%20an%20additional%20standard%20deduction%20of%20Rs%2075%2C000%20under%20the%20new%20regime.%20In%20practical%20terms%2C%20this%20will%20increase%20the%20exemption%20limit%20to%20Rs%2012%2C75%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Proposed%20Tax%20Slabs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20proposed%20a%20revised%20structure%20under%20which%20the%20tax%20slabs%20have%20been%20further%20broken%20down.%20The%20first%20slab%20is%20up%20to%20Rs%204%20lakh%2C%20in%20which%20the%20tax%20remains%20nil.%20Earlier%20it%20was%20Rs%203%20lakh.%20The%20next%20slab%20is%20Rs%204-8%20lakh%20where%20the%20tax%20rate%20is%205%25%2C%20followed%20by%2010%25%20in%20the%20Rs%208-12%20lakh%20slab%2C%2015%25%20in%20the%20Rs%2012-16%20lakh%20slab%2C%2020%25%20in%20the%20Rs%2016-20%20lakh%20slab%2C%20and%2025%25%20in%20the%20Rs%2020-24%20lakh%20slab.%20It's%20flat%2030%25%20above%20Rs%2024%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fluu55lq_tax-slabs_625x300_01_February_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Is%20Income%20Tax%20Calculated%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETax%20calculation%20follows%20a%20process%20that%20breaks%20down%20the%20total%20income%20into%20different%20slabs%2C%20which%20are%20then%20taxed%20at%20respective%20rates.%20This%20means%20one%20does%20not%20pay%20tax%20on%20the%20entire%20income%20at%20a%20flat%20rate.%20Neither%20is%20a%20salaried%20person%20taxed%20only%20on%20the%20remaining%20amount%20after%20the%20exempted%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fbudget-2025-income-tax-slabs-new-vs-old-tax-regimes-will-old-tax-regime-be-scrapped-budget-2025-sparks-speculation-7611159%5C%22%3EWill%20Old%20Tax%20Regime%20Be%20Scrapped%3F%20Budget%202025%20Sparks%20Speculation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20earn%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20annually%2C%20already%20excluding%20Rs%2075%2C000%20standard%20deduction%2C%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20the%20taxpayer%20will%20also%20enjoy%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20exemption%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fnfqgi8l8_gfx-2_625x300_01_February_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20taxation%20process%2C%20the%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20income%20will%20first%20be%20broken%20down%20and%20the%20first%20Rs%204%20lakh%20will%20be%20tax-free.%20A%20rate%20of%205%25%20will%20be%20applicable%20on%20the%20next%20Rs%204%20lakh%20(Rs%2020%2C000)%20under%20the%20Rs%204-8%20lakh%20slab.%20In%20Rs%208-12%20lakh%20slab%2C%20another%20Rs%204%20lakh%20will%20be%20taxed%20at%2010%25%20(Rs%2040%2C000).%20The%20remaining%20Rs%203%20lakh%20falls%20in%20the%20Rs%2012-16%20lakh%20slab%2C%20attracting%20a%20rate%20of%2015%25%2C%20which%20calculates%20to%20Rs%2045%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20adds%20up%20to%20Rs%201%2C05%2C000%20-%20which%20will%20be%20the%20total%20liability%20on%20a%20total%20taxable%20annual%20income%20of%20Rs%2015%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20The%20Rebate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tax%20benefit%20comes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20rebate.%20Even%20a%20salaried%20person%20earning%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20annually%20will%20be%20taxed%20as%20per%20the%20slabs.%20This%20means%2C%20the%20tax%20liability%20will%20stand%20at%20Rs%2060%2C000%2C%20which%20is%20the%20sum%20of%20Rs%200%20(Rs%200-4%20lakh%20at%20nil%20tax)%2C%20Rs%2020%2C000%20(Rs%204-8%20lakh%20at%205%25)%2C%20and%20Rs%2040%2C000%20(Rs%208-12%20lakh%20at%2010%25).%20But%20the%20government%20provides%20a%20full%20rebate%20of%20Rs%2060%2C000%2C%20making%20the%20total%20income%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20tax-free%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20taxpayer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20It%20Better%20Than%20Current%20Structure%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20someone%20with%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20total%20income%2C%20the%20total%20benefit%20increases%20to%20Rs%2080%2C000%2C%20which%20is%20the%20tax%20liability%20as%20per%20the%20existing%20structure.%20The%20shift%20from%20the%20existing%20slabs%20brings%20an%20additional%20relief%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000.%20This%20was%20one%20of%20the%20examples%20cited%20by%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20in%20her%20Budget%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-budget-2025-faqs-your-questions-on-new-income-tax-regime-answered-7610631%5C%22%3EFAQs%3A%20Government%20Answers%20Your%20Questions%20On%20New%20Income%20Tax%20Regime%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20take%20the%20example%20of%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20income.%20Under%20the%20current%20structure%2C%20the%20tax%20liability%20calculates%20to%20Rs%201.4%20lakh%20as%20against%20Rs%201.05%20lakh%20under%20the%20proposed%20slabs.%20This%20gives%20a%20slab%20relief%20of%20Rs%2035%2C000%20slab%20relief.%20There%20is%20no%20other%20exemption%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20It%20Better%20Than%20Old%20Regime%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20old%20regime%20allows%20exemptions%2C%20but%20the%20rates%20are%20higher.%20Since%20the%20Budget%20did%20not%20mention%20any%20change%20to%20the%20old%20regime%2C%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20assume%20that%20it%20remains%20unchanged.%20Under%20the%20old%20regime%2C%20any%20income%20above%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20was%20taxe