fs%20in%20O'Connell's%20kitchen%20cook%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20chanting%20monks.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20gone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprovidence-michelin-star-chef-kitchen-photos-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebehind%20the%20scenes%20of%20some%20legendary%20restaurants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I've%20never%20seen%20a%20kitchen%20as%20beautifully%20designed%20as%20the%20Inn%20at%20Little%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20cramped%20spaces%20and%20industrial%20silver%20as%20far%20as%20the%20eye%20can%20see%2C%20there%20are%20high%20ceilings%2C%20huge%20windows%2C%20and%20shimmering%20copper.%20The%20decorative%20blue%20and%20white%20tiles%20on%20the%20walls%20derive%20from%20an%20ancient%20tradition%20%E2%80%94%20O'Connell%20told%20me%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20thought%20that%20blue%20deterred%20flies%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20seen%20in%20the%20dairy%20room%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-royal-family-decorates-for-christmas-edinburgh-residence-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWindsor%20Castle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20the%20kitchen's%20design%20inspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20dinner%20service%20was%20in%20full%20swing.%20I%20watched%20as%20O'Connell's%20staff%20calmly%20plated%20delicate%20pieces%20of%20sashimi%20and%20piped%20%26quot%3BHappy%20Birthday%26quot%3B%20on%20white%20chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20O'Connell%20pointed%20to%20different%20stations%2C%20proudly%20introducing%20every%20cook%2C%20he%20told%20me%20they%20were%20planning%20the%20night's%20menu%20for%20a%20table%20of%20German%20tourists%20who%20were%20staying%20at%20the%20Inn%20for%2010%20nights%20and%20%26quot%3Bnever%20have%20the%20same%20thing%20twice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWritten%20under%20the%20kitchen's%20ceiling%20are%20five%20words%2C%20which%20O'Connell%20calls%20the%20five%20stages%20of%20dining.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inn%20at%20Little%20Washington%20kitchen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677db06750dfd88e193d5b28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWritten%20against%20a%20turquoise%20backdrop%20are%20%26quot%3BAnticipation%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BTrepidation%2C%20%26quot%3B%20the%20first%20two%20stages.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnticipation%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BTrepidation%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BInspection%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BFulfillment%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BEvaluation%26quot%3B%20are%20displayed%20across%20the%20kitchen%20to%20remind%20the%20staff%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20phase%20or%20stage%20the%20guest%20is%20at%20in%20any%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Connell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnticipation%2C%20the%20first%20stage%2C%20is%20one%20that%20O'Connell%20believes%20even%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20jaded%20diner%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20feels%20before%20they%20step%20into%20the%20dining%20room.%20Then%2C%20there's%20trepidation%2C%20when%20the%20guest%20is%20%26quot%3Bnaturally%20worried%20that%20it%20might%20not%20live%20up%20to%20their%20grandiose%20expectations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInspection%20likely%20begins%20after%20%26quot%3Bthe%20second%20sip%20of%20their%20first%20drink%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20the%20guest%20starts%20looking%20around%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20have%20any%20flaws%20stand%20out%20at%20that%20point%20because%20then%20it%20ruins%20the%20illusion%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Connell%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFulfillment%20tends%20to%20follow%20after%20the%20meat%20course%2C%20while%20evaluation%20begins%20after%20the%20final%20bite%20of%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20that%20we've%20succeeded%20is%20on%20their%20departure%20if%20they're%20talking%20about%20who%20they%20wish%20to%20bring%20on%20their%20next%20visit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chef%20explained.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20very%20rewarding%20to%20me%20when%20they%20say%2C%20'We%20need%20to%20bring%20our%20parents%20here%2C'%20because%20that's%20very%20personal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20my%20tour%20complete%2C%20O'Connell's%20famous%20show%20was%20about%20to%20begin.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221501%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anneta's%20table%20at%20Inn%20at%20Little%20Washington%20restaurant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677db0be50dfd88e193d5b2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221751%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20table%20in%20the%20sanctuary%20space%20of%20O'Connell's%20restaurant.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20led%20into%20the%20sanctuary%20through%20the%20warmly%20lit%20lounge%20and%20dining%20room%2C%20ornately%20decorated%20with%20scarlet%20drapes%2C%20pastel-pink%20chairs%2C%20and%20velvet%20blue%20booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lights%20were%20dim%2C%20casting%20shadows%20of%20the%20palm%20tree%20fronds%20that%20filled%20the%20space.%20A%20menu%20with%20my%20name%20on%20it%20was%20waiting%20for%20me%2C%20and%20the%20anticipation%20I'd%20been%20feeling%20for%20weeks%20was%20fully%20setting%20in.%20The%20first%20stage%20of%20dining%20had%20officially%20commenced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20waiter%20presented%20the%20first%20amuse-bouche%2C%20which%20he%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bworld's%20smallest%20grilled%20cheese.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inn%20at%20Little%20Washington%20dinner%20amuse%20bouche%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677db0e78951662c9f1f23a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20canap%C3%A9%20was%20presented%20on%20a%20plate%20designed%20to%20look%20like%20a%20tree%20trunk.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20canap%C3%A9%2C%20a%20delicious%20potato%20crisp%20filled%20with%20Parmesan%20and%20rolled%20in%20truffle%2C%20filled%20me%20with%20cheesy%20warmth.%20It%20was%20immediately%20followed%20by%20an%20oyster%20encased%20with%20an%20apple%20gel%C3%A9e%20and%20topped%20with%20Meyer%20lemon%20foam%2C%20a%20delightfully%20light%20and%20refreshing%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quick%20contrast%20of%20flavors%20and%20textures%20was%20as%20unexpected%20as%20Dolly%20Parton%20crooning%20through%20the%20hidden%20speakers.%20When%20I%20later%20told%20O'Connell%20I%20never%20expected%20to%20hear%20Dolly%20in%20a%20three-star%20Michelin%20restaurant%2C%20the%20chef%20told%20me%20he%20wanted%20to%20give%20a%20%26quot%3Bsense%20of%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20to%20be%20somebody's%20house%20and%20somebody's%20taste%2C%20so%20it%20has%20to%20be%20eclectic%2C%20and%20it%20can't%20be%20predictable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEach%20song%20is%20chosen%20to%20take%20you%20on%20a%20little%20journey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20came%20an%20adorable%20egg%20topped%20with%20cheese.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inn%20at%20Little%20Washington%20dinner%20amuse%20bouche%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677db13b50dfd88e193d5b3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20egg%20was%20filled%20with%20garlic%20custard%2C%20mushrooms%2C%20and%20a%20Parmesan%20foam.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20base%20of%20the%20egg%20was%20a%20roasted%20garlic%20custard%2C%20followed%20by%20saut%C3%A9ed%20cauliflower%20and%20chanterelle%20mushrooms%20topped%20with%20Parmesan%20foam%20and%20breadcrumbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filling%20was%20rich%20and%20silky