%20of%20the%20future.%20The%20establishment%20of%20five%20National%20Centres%20of%20Excellence%20for%20Skilling%2C%20the%20expansion%20of%20IIT%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20the%20Rs%20500%20crore%20allocation%20for%20AI%20in%20education%20will%20significantly%20enhance%20access%20to%20quality%20learning%20and%20industry-relevant%20training.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20fresh%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20Fund%20of%20Funds%20for%20startups%2C%20coupled%20with%20continued%20investments%20in%20manufacturing%20and%20innovation%2C%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20job%20creation%2C%20enabling%20India's%20youth%20to%20access%20new%20and%20diverse%20employment%20opportunities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrateek%20Shukla%2C%20Co-Founder%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%2C%20Masai%20School%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnion%20Budget%202025%20ensuring%20opportunities%20reach%20every%20section%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20addition%20of%2050%2C000%20Atal%20Tinkering%20Labs%20and%20broadband%20connectivity%20in%20government%20schools%20is%20a%20step%20toward%20democratising%20access%20to%20innovation%2C%20ensuring%20every%20child%E2%80%94regardless%20of%20background%E2%80%94has%20the%20opportunity%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20nation's%20growth.%20The%20expansion%20of%20medical%20education%20and%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Food%20Technology%20in%20Bihar%20will%20not%20only%20drive%20economic%20growth%20but%20also%20reinforce%20a%20culture%20of%20social%20responsibility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENipun%20Goenka%2C%20Managing%20Director%2C%20GD%20Goenka%20Group%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPolicies%20of%20Union%20Budget%202025%20must%20meet%20bold%20execution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Union%20Budget%202025-26%20sets%20the%20right%20direction%20with%20AI-driven%20education%2C%20research%20fellowships%2C%20deep-tech%20funding%2C%20and%20global%20skilling%20partnerships.%20These%20are%20crucial%20steps%20toward%20positioning%20education%20as%20an%20economic%20powerhouse.%20However%2C%20policy%20is%20always%20a%20work%20in%20progress%E2%80%94the%20real%20test%20is%20execution.%20If%20India%20is%20to%20leapfrog%20in%20education%20the%20way%20it%20did%20in%20digitization%2C%20we%20need%20a%2010X%20mindset%20in%20implementation%2C%20institutional%20accountability%2C%20and%20adaptability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunal%20Vasudeva%2C%20Co-founder%20%26amp%3B%20Managing%20Director%2C%20Indian%20School%20of%20Hospitality%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EInitiatives%20of%20the%20Union%20Budget%202025%20will%20prepare%20youth%20for%20international%20scale%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20establishment%20of%20the%20National%20Centres%20of%20Excellence%20for%20Skilling%20and%20the%20promotion%20of%20global%20skilling%20partnerships%20will%20empower%20the%20youth%20with%20skills%20pertinent%20to%20industry%20requirements%2C%20thereby%20enhancing%20their%20employability%20on%20an%20international%20scale.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20Centre%20of%20Excellence%20for%20AI%20in%20Education%20represents%20a%20significant%20leap%20forward%20in%20integrating%20artificial%20intelligence%20into%20educational%20frameworks.%20These%20initiatives%20align%20with%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20a%20globally%20competitive%20workforce.%20By%20focusing%20on%20these%20areas%2C%20India%20is%20not%20only%20addressing%20current%20educational%20needs%20but%20also%20preparing%20its%20youth%20for%20the%20evolving%20global%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnushika%20Jain%2C%20Founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20GlobalShala%20and%20Globally%20Recruit%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EUnion%20Budget%202025%20focuses%20on%20creating%20global%20leader%20in%20technology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20budget%20has%20a%20focus%20on%20inclusive%20growth%20and%20its%20potential%20to%20position%20India%20as%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20technology%20through%20in