aption%3E%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUS%20stock-market%20outperformance%20is%20due%20to%20end%2C%20says%20Bank%20of%20America's%20Michael%20Hartnett.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChinese%20AI%20firm%20DeepSeek%20challenges%20US%20tech-stock%20valuations%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPlus%2C%20a%20US%20fiscal%20slowdown%20and%20lower%20immigration%20rates%20pose%20risks%20to%20market%20performance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20days%20of%20the%20US%20stock%20market's%20outperformance%20on%20a%20global%20stage%20are%20about%20to%20end%2C%20Bank%20of%20America's%20top%20global%20strategist%20Michael%20Hartnett%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20exceptionalism%20now%20exceptionally%20expensive%2C%20exceptionally%20well-owned%2C%20outperformance%20to%20peak%20in%20'25%2C%26quot%3B%20Hartnett%20said%20in%20a%20client%20note%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHartnett%20laid%20out%20a%20three-point%20argument%20for%20why%20US%20stocks'%20outshining%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20may%20be%20over.%20One%20was%20the%20unexpected%20left%20hook%20that%20hit%20the%20US%20tech%20sector%20on%20Monday%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-deepseek-r1-china-ai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20AI%20firm%20released%20its%20R1%20chatbot%20to%20much%20fanfare%2C%20as%20it%20seemingly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-chatgpt-ai-retirement-investing-financial-advice-stock-market-openai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erivals%20ChatGPT's%20performance%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20significantly%20lower%20production%20price%20tag%20and%20more%20efficient%20energy%20usage.%20Investors%20were%20suddenly%20left%20questioning%20if%20all%20the%20money%20that%20tech%20firms%20were%20throwing%20at%20AI%20infrastructure%20was%20going%20to%20generate%20the%20kind%20of%20profits%20they%20were%20betting%20on.%20Hartnett%20thinks%20the%20answer%20is%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeepSeek%20means%20peak%20in%20AI%20capex%20return%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20reasons%20Hartnett%20is%20skeptical%20that%20US%20stocks%20can%20continue%20to%20beat%20their%20global%20counterparts%20are%20the%20slowdown%20in%20government%20spending%20he%20expects%20and%20lower%20immigration%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20fiscal%20spending%20has%20been%20well%20above%20trend%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20propel%20the%20market's%20outperformance%2C%20Hartnett%20argued.%20But%20since%20taking%20office%20on%20January%2020%2C%20President%20Trump%20has%20tried%20to%20issue%20a%20government%20spending%20halt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22us%20fiscal%20spending%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d2a80eb4be2fff9a32328%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221588%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20immigrants%20entering%20the%20US%20at%20the%20southern%20border%20has%20also%20sharply%20dropped%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20Hartnett%20highlighted%20that%20of%20the%20US%20population's%203.3%20million%20gain%20in%202024%2C%202.7%20million%20(84%25)%20were%20immigrants.%20And%20according%20to%20a%20Cato%20Institute%20analysis%20of%20Census%20Bureau%20data%2C%2078%25%20of%20job%20gains%20from%202019%20to%20March%202024%20were%20by%20immigrants.%20Lower%20immigration%20rates%20could%20slow%20job%20growth%20and%20hamper%20the%20economic%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221758%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22us%20border%20encounters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d2edf7bb3f854015b61e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221492%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20trends%20don't%20necessarily%20mean%20the%20broader%20market%20is%20set%20to%20crash%2C%20Hartnett%20said.%20Rather%2C%20the%20so-called%20Magnificent%20Seven%20is%20probably%20set%20to%20underperform%2C%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20market%20could%20benefit.%20The%20biggest%20risks%20facing%20the%20market%20are%20inflation%20and%20where%2010-year%20Treasury%20rates%20go%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariffs%20could%20prove%20trouble%20for%20inflation%20and%20rates%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20stocks.%20On%20Friday%2C%20major%20US%20stock%20indexes%20dropped%20after%20the%20White%20House%20announced%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%2C%20and%2010%25%20tariffs%20on%20China.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20fell%20more%20than%201%25%20in%20the%20last%20few%20hours%20of%20trading%2C%20while%2010-year%20yields%20climbed%20as%20much%20as%20eight%20basis%20points%2C%20from%204.5%25%20to%204.58%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6cc7be8-2a9f-4a91-b534-a96495f78ddd%5C%22%3E2%20trades%20outside%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20%26quot%3Bquiet%26quot%3B%20opportunities%20in%20global%20markets%20right%20now%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20%3Cstrong%3Ebank%20stocks%20in%20both%20Japan%20and%20Europe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Hartnett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20all-in%20on%20US%20exceptionalism%2C%20missing%20new%20secular%20bulls%20in%20cheap%2C%20unloved%20Japan%20%26amp%3B%20Europe%20banks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notoriously%20short-winded%20Hartnett%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BNote%20Japan%20banks%20still%2074%25%20below%201980s%20highs%20(Chart%204)%2C%20EU%20banks%2067%25%20below%202007%20highs%20(Chart%205)%2C%20and%20both%20breaking%20with%20upside%20likely%20in%20our%20view.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20the%20charts%20Hartnett%20is%20referring%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222744%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22japan%20and%20europe%20bank%20stocks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20