e%20demand%20for%20its%20GPU%20chips%2C%20which%20are%20the%20main%20fuel%20source%20for%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuppose%20large%20language%20models%20from%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmeta-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20adopt%20some%20of%20the%20techniques%20utilized%20by%20the%20open-sourced%20DeepSeek%20and%20become%20more%20efficient.%20Will%20they%20need%20as%20much%20computing%20power%20as%20initially%20thought%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20AI%20adopters%2C%20particularly%20software%20companies%2C%20surged%20on%20the%20prospect%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20AI%20technologies%20would%20decrease%20significantly%2C%20leading%20to%20higher%20profit%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20even%20broader%20lessons%20investors%20can%20take%20from%20this%20week's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-stock-crash-tech-selloff-ai-deepseek-black-swan-taleb-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblack%20swan%20event%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they%20impact%20everything%20from%20bonds%20to%20stocks%20and%20even%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c48a658c-9071-40db-9d4e-c66de8aee052%5C%22%3EWatch%20your%20concentration%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-selloff-deepseek-tech-ai-valuations-recession-nvda-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcentration%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20mega-cap%20tech%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20dominating%20the%20stock%20market%20has%20crept%20up%20to%20historic%20levels%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs%20data%2C%20the%20top%20five%20stocks%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20made%20up%20about%2029%25%20of%20the%20index%20as%20of%20December%2031%2C%20and%20they're%20all%20highly%20exposed%20to%20similar%20technology%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConcentration%20in%20several%20large%20names%20is%20a%20concern%20when%20the%20drivers%20of%20success%20are%20the%20same%20for%20most%20of%20the%20names%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Fasciano%2C%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20Commonwealth%20Financial%20Network%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConcentration%20is%20a%20double-edged%20sword.%20It%20can%20work%20great%20in%20bull%20markets%2C%20but%20a%20simple%20disruption%20to%20investors'%20overarching%20narrative%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20painful%20decline%2C%20as%20seen%20on%20Monday%2C%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fvanguard-mega-growth-index-fund-etf-shares-us9219108167%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindex%20tracking%3C%2Fa%3E%20mega-cap%20tech%20stocks%20plunged%203%25%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20slight%20gain%20for%20the%20equal-weighted%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concentration%20speaks%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20investors%20may%20not%20be%20as%20diversified%20as%20they%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20underappreciated%20consideration%2C%26quot%3B%20Steve%20Sosnick%2C%20chief%20strategist%20at%20Interactive%20Brokers%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20common%20%E2%80%94%20and%20understandable%20%E2%80%94%20for%20investors%20to%20believe%20that%20they%20are%20adequately%20diversified%20when%20they%20buy%20an%20S%26amp%3BP%20500-linked%20fund%2C%26quot%3B%20Sosnick%20said%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20case%20based%20on%20the%20extreme%20concentration%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20seeking%20true%20diversification%20need%20to%20look%20beyond%20SPX%2C%26quot%3B%20Sosnick%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Nasdaq%20is%20not%20the%20answer%2C%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20stocks%20making%20up%20about%20half%20of%20that%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5a4a6ac-f8ad-4495-b0f9-9d3ed8583e89%5C%22%3EThe%20AI%20story%20has%20layers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20has%20dominated%20the%20AI%20story%20since%20ChatGPT%20was%20released%20in%20November%202022%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-stock-ai-race-artificial-intelligence-wall-street-gpu-huang-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20turned%20into%20the%20key%20%26quot%3Bpicks%20and%20shovels%26quot%3B%20supplier%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20companies%20developing%20their%20own%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Monday's%20price%20action%20revealed%20that%20there%20are%20second-derivative%20beneficiaries%20to%20the%20AI%20trade%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20adopters%20of%20AI%20technologies%20like%20software%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20DeepSeek's%20claims%20of%20using%20less%20computing%20power%20are%20accurate%2C%20that%20means%20costs%20should%20come%20down%20considerably%20for%20AI%20adopters%2C%20pushing%20profit%20margins%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20software%20winners%20amid%20Monday's%20bloodbath%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fcrm-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalesforce%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20gained%20as%20much%20as%2010%25%20while%20the%20market%20swooned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20DeepSeek%20has%20truly%20shown%20us%20that%20an%20open-source%20solution%20is%20far%20less%20resource-dependent%20than%20the%20ChatGPT%20paradigm%2C%20then%20the%20benefits%20of%20AI%20might%20be%20easier%20to%20reap%20from%20companies%20unwilling%20or%20unable%20to%20afford%20to%20partner%20up%20with%20one%20of%20the%20current%20firms%20that%20currently%20dominate%20the%20arena%2C%26quot%3B%20Sosnick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220dce8106-d844-45f8-914b-d468bd27ca37%5C%22%3ECrypto%20is%20no%20safe%20haven%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto%20volatility%20was%20on%20full%20display%20this%20week%2C%20even%20though%20DeepSeek's%20appeared%20to%20mainly%20impact%20tech%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin%20dropped%20as%20much%20as%207%25%2C%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20sharp%20decline%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fnasdaq_100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENasdaq%20100.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sell-off%20highlights%20that%20cryptocurrencies%20are%20highly%20correlated%20to%20moves%20in%20the%20broader%20tech%20space%2C%20and%20absent%20any%20crypto-specific%20catalysts%2C%20bitcoin%20is%20a%20high-octane%20bet%20on%20tech's%20continued%20outperformance%20of%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSafe%20havens%20don't%20have%20an%20average%20daily%20volatility%20of%202%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Sosnick%20said.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%206%20months%2C%20the%20correlation%20of%20the%20price%20levels%20of%20bitcoin%20and%20NDX%20is%20about%2080%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225339dcfd-0027-4ff4-a1ac-53662ac17c23%5C%22%3EDon't%20count%20out%20Apple%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Faapl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20stock%20bucked%20the%20DeepSeek%20sell-off%2C%20rising%20about%208%25%20in%20the%20week%20as%20investors%20determined%20that%20the%20company's%20decision%20not%20to%20spend%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20on%20building%20its%20own%20large%20language%20model%20was%20a%20good%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Apple%20is%20focused%20on%20leveraging%20ChatGPT's%20AI%20model%20and%20using%20edge%20computing%20to%20deliver%20quick%20answers%20to%20iPhone%20users.%20That%20edge%20computing%20is%20key%2C%20as%20it%20could%20become%20even%20more%20ubiquitous%20if%20AI%20models%20see%20a%20decline%20in%20their%20compute%20consumption%20thanks%20to%20the%20breakthroughs%20identified%20by%20DeepSeek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20decline%20in%20compute%20consumption%20ultimately%20means%20a%20decline%20in%20costs%2C%20which%20could%20fuel%20even%20more%20stock%20buybacks%20and%20dividends%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCheap%20AI%20means%20a%20lot%20more%20capital%20to%20return%20to%20shareholders%2C%20either%20in%20the%20form%20of%20dividends%20or%20stock%20buybacks.%20Every%20US%20Big%20Tech%20company%20except%20Amazon%20already%20has%20both%20in%20place.%20Now%20they%20can%20get%20much%2C%20much%20bigger%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicholas%20Colas%2C%20co-founder%20of%20DataTrek%20Research%2C%20said%20in%20a%20note%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be3e4ee4-f0d0-41b9-aed4-7f90cd7d6af8%5C%22%3ECheap%20AI%20could%20fuel%20a%20bond%20market%20rally%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20DeepSeek's%20open-source%20model%20delivers%20the%20expected%20cost%20savings%20to%20other%20large%20language%20models%2C%20it%20could%20ultimately%20mean%20higher%20efficiency%20and%20lower%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20tech%20CEOs%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmsft-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Satya%20Nadella%2C%20cheap%20AI%20models%20should%20further%20accelerate%20the%20adoption%20of%20AI%20across%20various%20industries%20and%20lead%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy-roaring-20s-rapid-growth-stock-market-analysis-ed-yardeni-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurge%20in%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20happens%2C%20economic%20growth%20could%20continue%20without%20sparking%20a%20rebound%20in%20inflation%2C%20which%20would%20put%20interest%20rates%20back%20on%20a%20downward%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20DeepSeek's%20processes%20show%20that%20the%20AI%20revolution%20can%20be%20achieved%20at%20a%20lower%20cost%20and%20with%20lower%20energy%20usage%2C%20that%20would%20be%20good%20for%20macro%20conditions%20(such%20as%20productivity%20and%20inflation)%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20LPL%20chief%20strategist%20Jeff%20Buchbinder%20wrote%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BIn%20theory%2C%20this%20would%20help%20reduce%20the%20Fed's%20neutral%20rate%20a%20touch%20and%20keep%20interest%20rates%20lower%20than%20they%20otherwise%20would%20be%20if%20big%20AI%20spending%20continued%20unabated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20interest%20rates%20mean%20higher%20bond%20prices%2C%20sparking%20a%20potential%20rally%20in%20an%20asset%20class%20that%20was%20hurt%20by%20the%20Fed's%20rate%20hikes%20in%202022%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20egalitarian%20AI%20can%20and%20should%20boost%20productivity%20throughout%20the%20economy%20and%20thus%20have%20benefits%20for%20price%20levels%20and%20interest%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20Sosnick%20said%2C%20though%20he%20cautioned%20that%20such%20an%20outcome%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20going%20to%20happen%20immediately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-stock-crash-deepseek-lessons-ai-concentration-nvidia-bonds-crypto-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738404002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679cdef67bb3f854015b4ed1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftech-stock-crash-deepseek-lessons-ai-concentration-nvidia-bonds-crypto-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20the%20lessons%20from%20this%20week's%20tech%20plunge%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20heavy%20concentration%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20stocks%20is%20an%20important%20takeaway%20for%20investors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftech-stock-crash-deepseek-lessons-ai-concentration-nvidia-bonds-crypto-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Under%20the%20Shade%20of%20Trees%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Teacher%20Runs%20Open-Air%20School%20for%20Tribal%