porate%20tax%20collections%20had%20also%20added%20to%20the%20frustration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Middle%20Class's%20Energy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20budget%20offers%20a%20huge%20relief%20against%20many%20of%20these%20concerns.%20Announcing%20the%20revised%20tax%20structure%20applicable%20under%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%2C%20Sitharaman%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20middle%20class%20provides%20strength%20for%20India's%20growth.%20This%20government%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20has%20always%20believed%20in%20the%20admirable%20energy%20and%20ability%20of%20the%20middle%20class%20in%20nation-building.%20In%20recognition%20of%20their%20contribution%2C%20we%20have%20periodically%20reduced%20their%20tax%20burden%E2%80%A6Right%20after%202014%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98nil'%20tax%20slab%20was%20raised%20to%20Rs.%202.5%20lakh%2C%20which%20was%20further%20raised%20to%20Rs.%205%20lakh%20in%202019%20and%20to%20Rs.%207%20lakh%20in%202023.%20This%20is%20reflective%20of%20our%20government's%20trust%20in%20the%20middle-class%20taxpayers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20structure%20will%20substantially%20reduce%20the%20tax%20burden%20of%20the%20middle%20class.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20income%20tax%20payable%20on%20income%20of%20up%20to%20Rs.%2012%20lakhs.%20This%20limit%20will%20be%20Rs.%2012.75%20lakh%20for%20salaried%20taxpayers%20due%20to%20a%20standard%20deduction%20of%20Rs.%2075%2C000.%20The%20revised%20tax%20rate%20structure%20is%20as%20follows%3A%20nil%20tax%20for%20Rs.%200-4%20lakh%3A%20nil%2C%205%25%20for%20Ra%204-8%20lakh%2C%2010%25%20for%20Rs.%208-12%20lakh%2C%2015%25%20for%20Rs.%2012-16%20lakh%2C%2020%25%20for%20Rs.%2016-20%20lakh%2C%2025%25%20for%20Rs.%2020-%2024%20lakh%2C%20and%2030%25%20for%20income%20above%20Rs.%2024%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELose%20Some%2C%20Win%20Some%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20illustrate%2C%20a%20taxpayer%20in%20the%20new%20regime%20with%20an%20income%20of%20Rs.%2012%20lakh%20will%20get%20a%20benefit%20of%20Rs.%2080%2C000%20in%20tax%20(100%25%20of%20tax%20payable%20as%20per%20existing%20rates).%20For%20those%20earning%20more%20than%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20a%20year%2C%20tax%20slabs%20will%20kick%20in%20progressively.%20In%20effect%2C%20taxpayers%20earning%20Rs.%2012%20lakh%20can%20expect%20to%20save%20around%20Rs.%207%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20those%20earning%20Rs.%2018%20lakh%20will%20save%20around%20Rs.%206%2C000%2C%20and%20those%20earning%20Rs.%2025%20lakh%20may%20save%20around%20Rs.%209%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20these%20changes%2C%20the%20Central%20government%20will%20forgo%20Rs.%201%20lakh%20crore%20in%20direct%20taxes.%20However%2C%20the%20bulk%20of%20this%20money%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20taxpayers%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20spent%20on%20consumption%2C%20thus%20in%20a%20way%20leading%20to%20higher%20demand%20for%20goods%20and%20services.%20A%20section%20of%20this%20could%20also%20be%20recouped%20in%20the%20form%20of%20indirect%20taxes%2C%20such%20as%20GST%2C%20by%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20consumption%20accounts%20for%20more%20than%2060%25%20of%20India's%20GDP.%20However%2C%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20post-COVID-19%2C%20it%20had%20grown%20at%20a%20very%20slow%20pace%E2%80%94around%204%25%20in%20FY%202023-24%E2%80%94dragging%20the%20overall%20GDP%20growth%20down%20to%20a%206%25%20level.%20Without%20a%20consumption%20boost%2C%20it%20would%20be%20hard%20for%20the%20economy%20to%20return%20to%208%25%20GDP%20growth%20levels.%20The%20government%20perhaps%20realised%20this%2C%20that%20despite%20giving%20a%20tax%20break%20to%20the%20corporate%20sector%20in%202019%2C%20private%20investment%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20GDP%20had%20been%20sluggish.%20The%20government%20had%20so%20far%20been%20focusing%20on%20the%20supply%20side%20all%20these%20years%2C%20concentrating%20on%20boosting%20private%20investments%20that%20account%20for%20around%2030%25%20of%20the%20GDP%2C%20ignoring%20the%2060%25.%20Also%2C%20the%20private%20sector%20has%20long%20blamed%20low%20demand%20and%20low%20operating%20rates%2Fcapacity%20utilisation%20(in%20the%2070s)%20for%20their%20dull%20approach%20towards%20new%20investments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20Into%20Action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20with%20these%20tax%20breaks%2C%20the%20middle%20class%20is%20expected%20to%20get%20into%20action%20by%20consuming%20more%20and%20setting%20into%20motion%20a%20multiplier%20effect.%20The%20Rs.%201%20lakh%20crore%20stimulus%20is%20expected%20to%20provide%20a%20fillip%20to%20demand%2C%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20lead%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20operating%20rates%20and%20capacity%20utilisation%20of%20corporates.%20The%20increase%20in%20demand%20for%20goods%20and%20services%20will%20also%20kick%20in%20an%20investment%20cycle%2C%20providing%20a%20boost%20to%20GDP%20growth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcements%20are%20also%20politically%20significant%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections.%20It%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20woo%20the%20middle%20class%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20which%20tends%20to%20swing%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20party%20has%20long%20been%20targeting%20the%20AAP%20on%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Sheesh%20Mahal'%20controversy%20in%20order%20to%20rock%20the%20AAP's%20anti-corruption%20plank%20and%20sway%20its%20middle-class%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitically%2C%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20this%20budget%20could%20sway%20the%20kingmaker%20middle%20class%20in%20Delhi%20and%20propel%20it%20to%20power.%20And%2C%20on%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20the%20growth%20stimulus%20can%20provide%20the%20foundation%20for%20getting%20India%20back%20to%208%25%20GDP%20growth%20levels.%20It's%20a%20win-win.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738403460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fibnst4dg_budget_625x300_01_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Funion-budget-keeping-the-kingmaker-middle-class-happy-7610694%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20about%2031%25%20of%20India's%20population%20and%20makes%20up%20a%20core%20support%20block%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20was%20beginning%20to%20feel%20discontented%20due%20to%20the%20huge%20tax%20burden%20on%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Funion-budget-keeping-the-kingmaker-middle-class-happy-7610694%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUnion%20Budget%202025%20Will%20Be%20Applauded%20Abroad%20As%20Well%26quot%3B%3A%20Hardeep%20Puri%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Budget%202025%20is%20a%20holistic%20budget%20that%20will%20be%20applauded%20not%20only%20in%20India%20but%20abroad%20also%2C%20union%20minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20today.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20development%20budget%20which%20will%20lay%20a%20very%20solid%20step%20to%20Viksit%20Bharat%20(developed%20India)..%20it%20has%20something%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20budget%20has%20not%20only%20been%20welcomed%20in%20India%2C%20it%20will%20be%20welcomed%20outside.%20What%20are%20the%20people%20outside%20India%20looking%20at%3F%20They%20are%20looking%20at%20the%20gro