he%2032-year-old%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20commitment%20to%20providing%20value%20quickly%20earned%20him%20the%20loyalty%20of%20clients.%20Within%20the%20first%20year%2C%20the%20startup%20had%20secured%2040%20companies%20as%20customers.%20As%20the%20word%20spread%20about%20his%20affordable%20and%20eco-friendly%20packaging%2C%20the%20demand%20grew%20exponentially.%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20have%20around%20700%20companies%20as%20customers%20across%2060%20cities%20in%20India.%20Our%20major%20hubs%20include%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20Noida%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeveraging%20digital%20platforms%20for%20expansion%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20market%20his%20company%20and%20reach%20potential%20buyers%2C%20the%20founder%20leveraged%20digital%20platforms%20like%20IndiaMart%2C%20Justdial%2C%20and%20Exporter%20India.%20These%20platforms%20helped%20him%20connect%20with%20the%20right%20customers%20and%20expand%20his%20reach%20far%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20made%20600-700%20calls%20every%20month%2C%20and%20sometimes%20it%20took%20up%20to%20three%20months%20to%20convert%20a%20lead%20into%20a%20customer.%20But%20we%20remained%20consistent%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20made%20all%20the%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suhail%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20battling%20the%20early%20struggles%20with%20a%20well-planned%20strategy%2C%20Athar%20Packaging%20Solutions%20has%20been%20able%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20clients%2C%20including%20companies%20like%20Khadi%20Natural%2C%20Gopala%20Fresh%2C%20and%20Sai%20Expo%20Mart%2C%20as%20well%20as%20smaller%20businesses%20and%20self-help%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20our%20customers%2C%20Khadi%20Natural%2C%20started%20with%2010%2C000%20pouches%20in%20the%20pilot%20phase%2C%20and%20now%20they%E2%80%99re%20ordering%20